import math
T = int(input())
while T:
    a = [int(i) for i in input().split()]
    N = round(math.log(a[1], 2))
    fl = 0
    c = a[0] % a[1]
    for i in range(1, N + 3):
        c = c * c % a[1]
        if c == 0:
            fl = 1
            break
    if fl == 1:
        print('Yes')
    else:
        print('No')
    T = T - 1
